1. *Prekasno* je bilo da se sve popravi. (It was too late to fix everything.)
2. Neke stvari su se već dogodile *prekasno*. (Some things had already happened too late.)
3. Mislim da je *prekasno* za pomirenje. (I think it is too late for reconciliation.)
4. *Prekasno* sam shvatio svoju grešku. (I realized my mistake too late.)
5. *Prekasno* smo reagovali na situaciju. (We reacted to the situation too late.)
6. *Prekasno* sam shvatio da je to bila pogrešna odluka. (I realized too late that it was the wrong decision.)